  <brief_title>Open Versus Laparoscopically-assisted Esophagectomy for Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Open vs Laparoscopically-assisted Esophagectomy for Cancer: A Multicentric Phase III Prospective Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
